The access-filter enable command enables the iNOF host access interface whitelist function.
The undo access-filter enable command disables the iNOF host access interface whitelist function. The access-filter enable command enables the iNOF host access interface whitelist function. The undo access-filter enable command disables the iNOF host access interface whitelist function. By default, the iNOF host access interface whitelist function is disabled. This command is supported only on the CE6860-SAN, CE6866K, CE6866, CE6860-HAM, CE6885-SAN, CE8850-SAN, CE8851K, CE8851-32CQ8DQ-P and CE8850-HAM.
